The background appears to be a landscape with hills and a cloudy sky. The post is captioned "Monterey bay getaway with my Gorgeous Queen" along with several hashtags including #montereybay, #weekendgetaways, and #iloveyou.

The image shows a sign that says "Welcome to Dodgerfest" with the Los Angeles Dodgers logo and a Budweiser logo. The user's caption indicates they are a Dodgers fan.
The image shows a blue Subaru STI decorated with Christmas lights. It also has gold rims and underglow lighting.

The image shows two Subaru STIs at a gas station. One is red and the other is blue with Christmas lights and a tree on top. The post is captioned "12 days until Christmas" and includes hashtags like #christmas, #christmaslightsoncar, #subiexplug, #jdmfv, and #subieflow.
